<text><body>
<lb n="0835c09" ed="T"/>
<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<lb n="0835c10" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0835c11" ed="T"/><head type="no">No. 46 [No. 26(74), No. 125(41.6)]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0835c12" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead>佛說阿那律八念經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0835c13" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0835c14" ed="T"/><byline type="Translator">後漢<note n="0835004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">西域三藏＝三藏法師【三】</note><note n="0835004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">西域三藏＝三藏法師【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0835004"><lem wit="【大】">西域三藏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">三藏法師</rdg></app>支曜譯</byline>
<lb n="0835c15" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0835c1501">聞如是：</p><p id="pT01p0835c1504" place="inline">一時，佛在誓<note n="0835005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">牧＝枝【三】＊</note><note n="0835005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">牧＝枝【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0835005"><lem wit="【大】">牧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">枝</rdg></app>山求師樹下。賢者
<lb n="0835c16" ed="T"/>阿那律，在彼禪空澤中坐思惟言：「道法少欲，
<lb n="0835c17" ed="T"/>多欲非道；道法知足，無厭非道；道法隱處，樂
<lb n="0835c18" ed="T"/>眾非道；道法精進，懈怠非道；道法制心，放蕩
<lb n="0835c19" ed="T"/>非道；道法定意，多念非道；道法智慧，愚闇非
<lb n="0835c20" ed="T"/><note n="0835006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＋（道法捨家）【三】</note><note n="0835006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道＋（道法捨家）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0835006"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">道道法捨家</rdg></app>。」</p><p id="pT01p0835c2002" place="inline">佛以聖<note n="0835007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝&unrec;【三】</note><note n="0835007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心＝&unrec;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0835007"><lem wit="【大】">心</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&unrec;</rdg></app>逆知其意，譬如<note n="0835008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">力士＝壯人【三】</note><note n="0835008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">力士＝壯人【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0835008"><lem wit="【大】">力士</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">壯人</rdg></app>屈<note n="0835009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">申＝伸【三】</note><note n="0835009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">申＝伸【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0835009"><lem wit="【大】">申</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">伸</rdg></app>
<lb n="0835c21" ed="T"/>臂頃飛到其前，讚言：「善哉善哉！阿那律！汝
<lb n="0835c22" ed="T"/>所念者為大士念。聽吾語汝大士八念，善思
<lb n="0835c23" ed="T"/>行之。當學四禪撿意觀法而無中止，必獲大
<lb n="0835c24" ed="T"/>利，不失所願。何謂四禪？惟棄欲惡不善之法，
<lb n="0835c25" ed="T"/>意以歡喜，為一禪行。以捨惡念專心守一，不
<lb n="0835c26" ed="T"/>用歡喜，為二禪行。歡喜<note n="0835010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以止＝已正【三】</note><note n="0835010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以止＝已正【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0835010"><lem wit="【大】">以止</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">已正</rdg></app>，惟如法觀覺
<lb n="0835c27" ed="T"/>見苦樂，為三禪行。<note n="0835011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">又棄＝以捨【明】</note><app n="0835011"><lem wit="【大】">又棄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">以捨</rdg></app>苦樂，憂喜悉斷而住
<lb n="0835c28" ed="T"/>清淨，為四禪行。已學如是，而後惟行八大
<lb n="0835c29" ed="T"/>人念。四禪為撿意法，快見於行，得利願疾，
<pb n="0836a" ed="T" id="T01.0046.0836a"/>
<lb n="0836a01" ed="T"/>不復中止。又少欲者，其義譬如王有邊臣，主
<lb n="0836a02" ed="T"/>諸<note n="0836001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">椷＝函【元】【明】</note><app n="0836001"><lem wit="【大】">椷</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">函</rdg></app>簏滿中綵衣，而汝自樂著&CB00308;弊者，少
<lb n="0836a03" ed="T"/>欲知足，隱處精進，制心定意，智慧捨家，不
<lb n="0836a04" ed="T"/>以戲慢，無有差跌，必安隱人，至泥洹門。是
<lb n="0836a05" ed="T"/>八大人念，惟四禪撿意觀法，其義譬如王有
<lb n="0836a06" ed="T"/>邊臣，監主&CB00634;宰和調五味，而汝自樂乞食，
<lb n="0836a07" ed="T"/>趣得救身不以快心。其義譬如王有遊觀樓
<lb n="0836a08" ed="T"/>閣，而汝自樂山澤樹間<note n="0836002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">燕＝宴【三】</note><note n="0836002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">燕＝宴【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836002"><lem wit="【大】">燕</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">宴</rdg></app>處精進，無欲於
<lb n="0836a09" ed="T"/>世。其義譬如王有邊臣，主諸良藥及酪<note n="0836003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">酥＝蘇【宋】</note><app n="0836003"><lem wit="【大】">酥</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">蘇</rdg></app>
<lb n="0836a10" ed="T"/><note n="0836004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">醍醐＝&CB01172;餬【宋】</note><app n="0836004"><lem wit="【大】">醍醐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&CB01172;餬</rdg></app>石蜜，而汝自樂有疾以服，小便<note n="0836005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">趣＝取【三】</note><note n="0836005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">趣＝取【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836005"><lem wit="【大】">趣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">取</rdg></app>得
<lb n="0836a11" ed="T"/>除惱。以行八念，思惟四禪，精進不虧，心無
<lb n="0836a12" ed="T"/>差跌，必自安隱至泥洹門。」</p>
<lb n="0836a13" ed="T"/><p id="pT01p0836a1301">佛說是已，即還誓<app type="＊" source="0835005"><lem wit="【大】">牧</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">枝</rdg></app>告諸弟子：「道當少欲，
<lb n="0836a14" ed="T"/>無得多欲；道當知足，無<note n="0836006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畜＝蓄【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0836006"><lem wit="【大】">畜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">蓄</rdg></app>遺餘；道當隱處，
<lb n="0836a15" ed="T"/>無樂眾會；道當精進，無得懈怠；道當制心，無
<lb n="0836a16" ed="T"/>得放逸；道當定意，無得亂念；道當智慧，無得
<lb n="0836a17" ed="T"/>愚闇。</p><p id="pT01p0836a1703" place="inline">「比丘當少欲者快，謂身自少欲，不使
<lb n="0836a18" ed="T"/>眾人知我少欲，義當從是。</p><p id="pT01p0836a1811" place="inline">「比丘知足，謂應
<lb n="0836a19" ed="T"/>器<note n="0836007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法衣＝衣服【三】</note><note n="0836007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">法衣＝衣服【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836007"><lem wit="【大】">法衣</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">衣服</rdg></app>&CB00646;臥<note n="0836008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">病＝疾【三】</note><note n="0836008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">病＝疾【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836008"><lem wit="【大】">病</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">疾</rdg></app>藥，得食足止，不<app type="＊" source="0836006"><lem wit="【大】">畜</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">蓄</rdg></app>遺餘，
<lb n="0836a20" ed="T"/>義當從是。</p><p id="pT01p0836a2005" place="inline">「比丘隱處，謂避人間，不入眾會，
<lb n="0836a21" ed="T"/>遠居山澤巖石樹間。如有四輩，若王大臣來
<lb n="0836a22" ed="T"/>從問道，為說清淨欲令疾去。譬如貧人負豪
<lb n="0836a23" ed="T"/>姓債，為主所牽<note n="0836009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">抴＝拽【三】</note><note n="0836009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">抴＝拽【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836009"><lem wit="【大】">抴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">拽</rdg></app>，欲離不樂潛隱遠<note n="0836010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遁＝眾【三】</note><note n="0836010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遁＝眾【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836010"><lem wit="【大】">遁</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">眾</rdg></app>，義
<lb n="0836a24" ed="T"/>當從是。</p><p id="pT01p0836a2404" place="inline">「比丘精進，謂斷非法，勤行經道未
<lb n="0836a25" ed="T"/>常懈<note n="0836011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惓＝倦【三】</note><note n="0836011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惓＝倦【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836011"><lem wit="【大】">惓</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">倦</rdg></app>，上中後夜經行坐臥，常覺寤意念
<lb n="0836a26" ed="T"/>淨以除五蓋，義當從是。</p><p id="pT01p0836a2610" place="inline">「比丘制心，棄欲惡
<lb n="0836a27" ed="T"/>法，坐意惟觀，以斷苦樂，得四禪行，義當從
<lb n="0836a28" ed="T"/>是。</p><p id="pT01p0836a2802" place="inline">「比丘定意，謂常一心，觀身觀意觀法，不
<lb n="0836a29" ed="T"/>為猗行，攝念就道捨癡惱想，義當從是。</p><p id="pT01p0836a2916" place="inline">「比
<pb n="0836b" ed="T" id="T01.0046.0836b"/>
<lb n="0836b01" ed="T"/>丘智慧，謂知四諦：苦．<note n="0836012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">習＝集【元】【明】＊</note><app n="0836012"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>．盡．道。何謂苦諦？生
<lb n="0836b02" ed="T"/>苦、老苦、病苦、死苦、憂悲惱苦、恩愛別苦、怨
<lb n="0836b03" ed="T"/>憎會苦、所欲不得苦、合五盛陰苦。生苦者，
<lb n="0836b04" ed="T"/>謂人隨行所墮，受胞成生，已出形現，根入受
<lb n="0836b05" ed="T"/>長。老者，謂人根熟形變，髮白齒落、筋緩皮
<lb n="0836b06" ed="T"/>皺、僂步<note n="0836013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">拄＝柱【宋】【元】</note><app n="0836013"><lem wit="【大】">拄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">柱</rdg></app>杖。病者，謂人罪行所致，<note n="0836014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">癰疽＝疽癰【三】</note><note n="0836014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">癰疽＝疽癰【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836014"><lem wit="【大】">癰疽</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">疽癰</rdg></app>瘡
<lb n="0836b07" ed="T"/>膿&CB00678;癲長病，亦百餘種。死者，謂人命逝形
<lb n="0836b08" ed="T"/>壞，溫消氣絕魂神離逝。是<note n="0836015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＝比【三】</note><note n="0836015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆＝比【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836015"><lem wit="【大】">皆</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">比</rdg></app>為苦。何謂
<lb n="0836b09" ed="T"/><app type="＊" source="0836012"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>諦？<note n="0836016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔謂〕－【三】</note><note n="0836016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔謂〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836016"><lem wit="【大】">謂</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&lac;</rdg></app>婬心樂喜而生恩愛，<note n="0836017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">志＝至【元】【明】，〔志〕－【宋】</note><app n="0836017"><lem wit="【大】">志</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">至</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">&lac;</rdg></app>在貪欲，令
<lb n="0836b10" ed="T"/>復有漏，眾行滋盛以著自縛。所謂愛者，眼
<lb n="0836b11" ed="T"/>愛色、耳愛聲、鼻愛香、舌愛味、身愛細滑、心愛
<lb n="0836b12" ed="T"/>所欲；但觀其常樂在望，安以為利，呼言是
<lb n="0836b13" ed="T"/>我有，以著自縛，從是故色痛想行識五陰<note n="0836018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愛＝受【三】</note><note n="0836018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愛＝受【宋】【元】【明】<app><lem resp="CBETA.say">＊</lem><rdg wit="【大】"></rdg></app></note><app n="0836018"><lem wit="【大】">愛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">受</rdg></app>
<lb n="0836b14" ed="T"/>盛，見常貪樂，謂是我有，以著自縛。所謂色
<lb n="0836b15" ed="T"/>者，精神所受地氣、水氣、火氣、風氣，變化為
<lb n="0836b16" ed="T"/>形；以所愛著，令眼識色、耳識聲、鼻識香、舌識
<lb n="0836b17" ed="T"/>味、身識細滑、意識法著，<note n="0836019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">信＝作【三】</note><note n="0836019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">信＝作【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836019"><lem wit="【大】">信</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">作</rdg></app>為<app type="＊" source="0836012"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>諦。何謂
<lb n="0836b18" ed="T"/>盡諦？不受不入，愛盡無餘，縛著已解，如慧
<lb n="0836b19" ed="T"/>見者，不復有一切故。世間人<note n="0836020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＋（入）【三】</note><note n="0836020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">無＋（入）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836020"><lem wit="【大】">無</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">無入</rdg></app>所見，五陰
<lb n="0836b20" ed="T"/>所著；計數已盡，愛縛都解，已從慧見非常、苦、
<lb n="0836b21" ed="T"/>空、非身故斷，是為盡諦。何謂道諦？謂八直
<lb n="0836b22" ed="T"/>道，正見、正思、正言、正行、正治、正命、正志、正定。
<lb n="0836b23" ed="T"/>何謂正見？正見有二：有俗、有道。知有仁義，
<lb n="0836b24" ed="T"/>知有父母，知有沙門梵志，知有得道真人，
<lb n="0836b25" ed="T"/>知有今世後世，知有善惡罪福，從此到彼以
<lb n="0836b26" ed="T"/>行為證，是為世間正見。<note n="0836021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】＊</note><note n="0836021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】＊【元】＊【明】＊</note><app n="0836021"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>解四諦：苦．<app type="＊" source="0836012"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>．盡．
<lb n="0836b27" ed="T"/>道，已得慧見，空淨非身，是為道正見。正思
<lb n="0836b28" ed="T"/>亦有二：思學問、思和敬、思誡慎、思無害，是為
<lb n="0836b29" ed="T"/>世間正思；思出處、思忍默、思滅愛盡著，<note n="0836022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（數）＋是【三】</note><note n="0836022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（數）＋是【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836022"><lem wit="【大】">是</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">數是</rdg></app>
<pb n="0836c" ed="T" id="T01.0046.0836c"/>
<lb n="0836c01" ed="T"/>為道正思。正言亦有二：<note n="0836023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＋（漫）【三】</note><note n="0836023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＋（漫）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836023"><lem wit="【大】">不</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">不漫</rdg></app>兩舌、不惡罵、不
<lb n="0836c02" ed="T"/>妄言、不綺語，是為世間正言；離口四<note n="0836024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">過＝惡【三】</note><note n="0836024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">過＝惡【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836024"><lem wit="【大】">過</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">惡</rdg></app>，講
<lb n="0836c03" ed="T"/>誦道語，心不造為，盡無復餘，是為道正言。
<lb n="0836c04" ed="T"/>正行亦有二：身行善、口言善、心念善，是為世
<lb n="0836c05" ed="T"/>間正行；身口精進，心念空淨，消蕩滅著，是
<lb n="0836c06" ed="T"/>為道正行。正治亦有<note n="0836025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＋（身）【三】</note><note n="0836025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二＋（身）【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836025"><lem wit="【大】">二</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">二身</rdg></app>：不殺盜婬，不自貢
<lb n="0836c07" ed="T"/>高，修德自守，是為世間正治；離身三惡，除
<lb n="0836c08" ed="T"/>斷苦<app type="＊" source="0836012"><lem wit="【大】">習</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">集</rdg></app>，滅<app type="＊" source="0836018"><lem wit="【大】">愛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">受</rdg></app>求度，是為道正治。正命亦
<lb n="0836c09" ed="T"/>有二：求財以道不貪苟得，不詐<note n="0836026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">紿＝怠【三】</note><note n="0836026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">紿＝怠【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836026"><lem wit="【大】">紿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">怠</rdg></app>心於人，
<lb n="0836c10" ed="T"/>是為世間正命；<note n="0836027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】</note><note n="0836027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836027"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">已</rdg></app>離邪業，捨世占候，不犯
<lb n="0836c11" ed="T"/>道禁，是為道正命。正志亦有二：不<note n="0836028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">嫉&CB00107;＝&CB00107;嫉【三】</note><note n="0836028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嫉&CB00107;＝&CB00107;嫉【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836028"><lem wit="【大】">嫉&CB00107;</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00107;嫉</rdg></app>、不
<lb n="0836c12" ed="T"/>恚怒、不事邪，是為世間正<note n="0836029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">念＝志【明】</note><note n="0836029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">念＝志【明】【CB】</note><app n="0836029"><lem resp="CBETA.maha" cf1="T01n0046_p0836c11" wit="【CBETA】">志</lem><rdg wit="【大】">念</rdg><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">志</rdg></app>；離心三惡，行
<lb n="0836c13" ed="T"/>四意端，清淨無為，是為道正志。正定亦有
<lb n="0836c14" ed="T"/>二：性體淳調，安善安固，心不邪曲，是為世
<lb n="0836c15" ed="T"/>間正定；得四意志，惟空、無想、不願，見泥洹<note n="0836030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">源＝原【三】</note><note n="0836030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">源＝原【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836030"><lem wit="【大】">
<lb n="0836c16" ed="T"/>源</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">原</rdg></app>，是為道正定，是為道諦。比丘捨家棄捐
<lb n="0836c17" ed="T"/>恩愛，安靜思道無所戀慕，意不隨欲淨無罣
<lb n="0836c18" ed="T"/>礙，是為<note n="0836031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">道＝隨【宋】【元】</note><app n="0836031"><lem wit="【大】">道</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】">隨</rdg></app>法，義當從是。」</p><p id="pT01p0836c1810" place="inline">賢者阿那律聞佛
<lb n="0836c19" ed="T"/>說經，開導其意受行三月，漏盡意解，得三治
<lb n="0836c20" ed="T"/>以為證已，自覺得羅漢，便說偈<note n="0836032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">言＝曰【三】</note><note n="0836032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">言＝曰【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836032"><lem wit="【大】">言</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">曰</rdg></app>：</p>
<lb n="0836c21" ed="T"/><lg id="lgT01p0836c2101" rend="margin-left:1em;text-indent:-1em"><l>「夫欲而無厭，</l><l>樂眾以<note n="0836033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">放＝故【三】</note><note n="0836033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">放＝故【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836033"><lem wit="【大】">放</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">故</rdg></app>意，</l>
<lb n="0836c22" ed="T"/><l>是行<note n="0836034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝後【三】</note><note n="0836034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝後【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836034"><lem wit="【大】">以</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">後</rdg></app>致苦，</l><l>修惡多所著。</l>
<lb n="0836c23" ed="T"/><l>少欲知道行，</l><l>知慚不自見，</l>
<lb n="0836c24" ed="T"/><l>是法墮清淨，</l><l>遠惡致度世。</l>
<lb n="0836c25" ed="T"/><l>道意不貪生，</l><l>亦無樂死<note n="0836035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">別＝想【三】</note><note n="0836035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">別＝想【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836035"><lem wit="【大】">別</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">想</rdg></app>，</l>
<lb n="0836c26" ed="T"/><l>吾以如空定，</l><l>諸苦得待時。</l>
<lb n="0836c27" ed="T"/><l>從佛受教<note n="0836036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝令【三】</note><note n="0836036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">命＝令【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0836036"><lem wit="【大】">命</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">令</rdg></app>，</l><l>守行棄欲惡，</l>
<lb n="0836c28" ed="T"/><l>所身患<app type="＊" source="0836021"><lem wit="【大】">已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">以</rdg></app>捨，</l><l>得利就無為。</l>
<lb n="0836c29" ed="T"/><l>自致至三治，</l><l>已拔恩愛根，</l>
<pb n="0837a" ed="T" id="T01.0046.0837a"/>
<lb n="0837a01" ed="T"/><l>當於維沙<note n="0837001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">聚＝&CB00448;【三】</note><note n="0837001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">聚＝&CB00448;【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0837001"><lem wit="【大】">聚</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">&CB00448;</rdg></app>，</l><l>竹園般泥洹。」</l></lg>
<lb n="0837a02" ed="T"/><juan n="001" fun="close"><jhead>佛說阿那律八念經</jhead></juan>
</div1></body></text></TEI.2>